# 0. Simple web stack

Diagram: https://imgur.com/a/byjQaM8

Explanation:
- User requests www.foobar.com
- DNS resolves to 8.8.8.8 (A record)
- Server hosts Nginx, app server, code, and MySQL
- Communication is via HTTP/HTTPS over TCP
- SPOF: one server only
- Maintenance requires downtime
- Cannot scale traffic
